{
  "texts": [
    "In other words, the PTQ-QLoRA integration can match and in many cases outperform 16-bit full fine-tuning in our target task performance.",
    "(ii) Applying quantization with without additional QLoRA step does not significantly affect factual consistency on text generation tasks.",
    "(iii) In nearly all tasks, incorporating the QLoRA process enhances the accuracy of PTQ, regardless of the base model or the quantization method employed.",
    "(iv) Between the two quantization methods used in our experiments (BNB and GPTQ), we do not find a clear advantage of one method over the other.",
    "The relative performance difference can be affected by the base pre-trained model or the target task."
  ]
}